When you grew up,

153
00:07:37,456 --> 00:07:39,696
Liu Chengfeng replaced you as Cui Lin

154
00:07:39,815 --> 00:07:41,136
and became my son.

155
00:07:43,336 --> 00:07:44,935
You're a lady.

156
00:07:45,055 --> 00:07:46,615
