165
00:08:05,055 --> 00:08:06,415
I love going to war.

166
00:08:06,495 --> 00:08:07,776
I love to live this way.

167
00:08:08,230 --> 00:08:09,735
There are plenty of men in the world.

168
00:08:09,896 --> 00:08:11,055
