233
00:10:36,696 --> 00:10:38,096
Do not let him escape.

234
00:10:38,096 --> 00:10:38,696
Yes!

235
00:10:43,535 --> 00:10:44,416
Don't come near me!

236
00:10:45,056 --> 00:10:46,096
All of you, stay put!

237
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,790
