245
00:11:28,096 --> 00:11:28,895
Uncle,

246
00:11:29,615 --> 00:11:31,056
I had no choice!

247
00:11:34,255 --> 00:11:35,696
Uncle, don't come near me!

248
00:11:36,296 --> 00:11:37,576
