278
00:13:28,096 --> 00:13:28,816
Come here.

279
00:13:32,535 --> 00:13:34,015
Father, can I join in too?

280
00:13:34,015 --> 00:13:34,735
Of course.

281
00:13:34,735 --> 00:13:36,135
You're my son too.

282
00:13:36,296 --> 00:13:37,416
